<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.8.3">
<l>vācakamē yētta varuḷceyum vāṉavartan</l>
<l>nāyakaṉē nāḷiḷan tiṅkaḷaik kōḷviṭuttu</l>
<l>vēyakam pālveṇṇey toṭuvuṇṭa vāṉāyar</l>
<l>tāyavaṉē yeṉṟu taṭavumeṉ kaikaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O leader of the celestials who does grace while the speech praises,</l>
<l>o the one who leapt over the cowherders who touched [and] ate</l>
<l>the milk [and] butter inside the bamboo, releasing the hold</l>
<l>on the day-young moon”, [thus] fumble my hands.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
